<quest id="targetPractice" name="Boot Camp" startsAt="commander" endsAt="commander"
    level="1"
    brief="Welcome to the front, soldier!  I'm your commanding officer here.  I trust you know how to use that gun?
    Head to the range and shoot a few targets.  Make sure your equipment still works."
    debrief="Well the gun works, but those wheels aren't quite cut out for the fight ahead.  Here's an upgrade.
    I think you're ready to see some action!" >
    <objective type="kill" id="practiceTarget" qty="3" />
    <reward type="item" id="tankTracks" />
</quest>
<quest id="killEnemies" name="A Taste of Blood" startsAt="commander" endsAt="engineer"
    level="2"
    brief="We've got a beachhead here, but can't hold it forever.  We need to advance.
    There are enemy forces to the East, but that's our path forward.  Take out as many as you can, and press through to the river.  Your contact there is an engineer, name of Bruce.
    Oh, and soldier?  Try not to get killed out there."
    debrief="G'day!  Stoked you made it through; I was starting to think that yank officer would never send any support." >
    <prerequisite id="targetPractice" />
    <objective type="kill" id="enemy" qty="4" />
    <reward type="item" id="chassisTank" />
</quest>
<quest id="buildBridge" name="Troubled Waters" startsAt="engineer" endsAt="engineer"
    level="3"
    brief="The enemy base is across this river.  It's too deep to drive through, so I reckon we'll need to bridge it.
    Grab some wood from these trees, then have a go at building a bridge."
    debrief="You beauty!  Should just be a quick trip up the road now to take out the base.  Here's a proper gun to do the job.
    Catch you afterwards for a cold one, mate?" >
    <objective type="construct" id="bridge" />
    <reward type="item" id="cannon" />
</quest>

